# `warning` will detect with `make fmt` (needs manual fix)
# NOTE:
#   Potentially destructive diagnostics should be fixed manually.
#   But we mark them `warning` severity.
#   Because when running `dotnet format --severity warn`, it also detects and auto-fixes `error` level diagnostics.
#   This design allows safe auto-fixes at `error` level while requiring manual review for `warning` level changes
#   that might alter code behavior or require careful consideration.
